skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: city of tamarac
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This is the official Alexa skill for the City of Tamarac Florida. Learn more about the City, check out upcoming calendar events, or even ask Alexa to speak to any of our City departments, divisions or offices for more inquiries. 

List of Features Include:
Play my notifications
Calendar Events
Local events happening on a specific date
Are there any events next week?
Pay my water bill
Customer Service
Ask Tamarac "any city-related question"
